query:
SELECT 
  ai.id,
  ai.auditTypeId,
  at.auditName,
  ai.auditTemplateId,
  atem.templateName
FROM auditInstances ai
JOIN auditTypes at ON ai.auditTypeId = at.id
LEFT JOIN auditTemplates atem ON ai.auditTemplateId = atem.id
WHERE at.auditName LIKE '%Daily%'
ORDER BY ai.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 3;
